	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. Load SCL_Main_A.&#xD;&#xA;2. Have Karlach in your party.&#xD;&#xA;3. In the debug book set up the tiefling path.&#xD;&#xA;4. goto -8; 28; 119&#xD;&#xA;4.5. If in editor: oe havchec&#xD;&#xA;5.  Go through the checkpoint dialog, it should trigger after it if Karlach is near and available." />
